metadata.name: inizio
metadata.description:
As a token (hehe pun) of my appreciation for minting "The State of Mental Health", please enjoy inizio (beginning in Italian.) 

We went through a lot last year, 2022 was one of the most difficult years in my life. I am looking forward to moving on, working more on myself, creating more art, connecting with more people and embark on new journeys.

Thank you for believing in me.
